&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and close high-value, complex enterprise opportunities, consistently meeting or exceeding individual quotas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build a strategic pipeline through self-prospecting, account planning, and SDR partnership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively identify whitespace, expansion potential, and multi-entity opportunities within target accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain forecasting, opportunity hygiene, and deal governance in Salesforce (SFDC).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strategic Discovery &amp;amp; Solution Architecture&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead executive-level discovery to understand enterprise supply chain strategy, risk posture, and long-term business objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate complex buying groups across procurement, ops, finance, IT, and senior leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design integrated, multi-product Flexport solutions aligned to customer priorities and business outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Position Flexport as a strategic partner through compelling value narratives, business cases, and solution roadmaps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Deal Strategy, Negotiation &amp;amp; Closing&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own end-to-end deal strategy for complex opportunities, including stakeholder mapping, decision criteria, and close plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead advanced commercial negotiation, pricing, contracts, and non-standard deal structures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Orchestrate internal stakeholders (Ops, Finance, Legal, Product) to progress deals efficiently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Onboarding, Expansion &amp;amp; Relationship Leadership&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the onboarding motion, ensuring enterprise customers are set up for scalable success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and maintain trusted relationships with senior and executive customer stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify expansion opportunities together with Account Management to drive sustained growth.&lt;/li&gt;
