&lt;p&gt;The Enterprise Account Executive is responsible for acquiring and developing net-new enterprise customers through a structured, consultative sales process. This role focuses on managing moderately complex sales cycles involving multiple stakeholders, longer decision timelines, and tailored solutions. The AE owns the full sales cycle from prospecting through close and initial onboarding, partnering closely with SDRs and cross-functional teams to deliver value-driven enterprise solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your responsibilities as an&lt;strong&gt; Account Executive, ENT &lt;/strong&gt;include, but are not limited to the following:&lt;/p&gt;
