&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the future!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will be:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building and growing Flexport Italy together with your colleagues, our ambitions are high!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifying good fit clients - both self-prospected and generated by your SDR team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consulting with new clients to understand their supply chain needs and pains&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creating a value add solution, demonstrating our capabilities through remote and in-person meetings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Closing the deal - that goes without saying!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leading the customer onboarding process by leveraging internal resources and teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ll be joining a sales team with a lot of emphasis on growth, combining great culture, a place to succeed and focus on career development make this a fun &amp;amp; dynamic place to work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
