&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s or Master’s degree.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3–5 years of Account Management experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An entrepreneurial mindset with a strong track record of successfully delivering innovation and driving results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working within complex global organizations and collaborating across cross-functional teams to drive business outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building global client relationships and leveraging those relationships to grow strategic partnerships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for team success with the ability to inspire and motivate others.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;

